<lb ed="B" n="0314a11"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="36"><cb:jhead>金陵梵剎志卷三十六</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="B" n="0314a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">永興寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">中剎</note>永興寺　<note place="inline">勅賜</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0314a13"/><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1301" style="margin-left:1em">在都門外南城地北去所綂報恩寺三里聚寶門三里
<lb ed="B" n="0314a14"/>下梅岡西南成化初年賜額林壑幽閴<g ref="#CB02420"/>制甚麗今<note n="0314a1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【補編】</note><app n="0314a1401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">巳</rdg></app>
<lb ed="B" n="0314a15"/>近<note n="0314a1501" resp="CBETA" type="add">圮【CB】，圯【補編】</note><app n="0314a1501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">圮</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">圯</rdg></app>所領小剎曰普照寺惠應寺安隱院</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0314a16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1603" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">壹座</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">金剛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1607" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">金剛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">天王殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1612" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">天王殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1617" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左伽藍殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1621" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左伽藍殿<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0314a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右祖師殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1701" style="margin-left:2em">右祖師殿<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">鐘鼓樓</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1707" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">鐘鼓樓<note place="inline">貳座</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1712" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">肆房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址貳拾伍畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1716" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址貳拾伍畆<note place="inline">東至官街
<lb ed="B" n="0314a18"/>　南至范家山　西至寶光寺　北至禮拜寺</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0314a19"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><head>【公產】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">田地山塘</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314a1903" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">田地山塘<note place="inline">共貳百肆畆叄分伍厘</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0314a20"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">普照寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>普照寺<note place="inline">古剎　勅賜</note></head>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0314b" n="0314b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0314b01"/><p xml:id="pB29p0314b0101" style="margin-left:1em">在都門外南城西去所領永興寺半里北去聚寶門二
<lb ed="B" n="0314b02"/>里舊名菴元至大間僧無盡建成化間僧定瑀重建
<lb ed="B" n="0314b03"/>　賜額</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0314b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b0403" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">壹座</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">天王殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b0407" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">天王殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b0412" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左右廻廊</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b0416" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左右廻廊<note place="inline">拾肆楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">毘盧殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b0423" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">毘盧殿
<lb ed="B" n="0314b05"/><note place="inline">伍楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b0503" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">拾肆房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">禪堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b0508" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">禪堂<note place="inline">伍楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址伍畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b0512" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址伍畆<note place="inline">東至王駙馬墳　南至惠應寺　西至未
<lb ed="B" n="0314b06"/>異寺園溝　北至官街</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0314b07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">文</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">【文】</note></head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">普照寺重修前殿記略</cb:mulu><head>普照寺重修前殿記略</head><byline cb:type="author">明南刑部郎平定白鑑</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0314b08"/><p xml:id="pB29p0314b0801">普照故菴也不知創自何代至大間僧人無盡重建入我
<lb ed="B" n="0314b09"/>聖朝又餘百年矣成化甲辰沙門定瑀號寶山者歷訪名
<lb ed="B" n="0314b10"/>山足跡將半天下晚遊<g ref="#CB12428"/>都偶至是菴風景持異遂經理
<lb ed="B" n="0314b11"/>定居焉以次修緝菴之名猶故也正德丁丑寶山以僧行
<lb ed="B" n="0314b12"/>薦　詔昇菴為寺寶山遷右講經嘉靖改元仍於故基大
<lb ed="B" n="0314b13"/>建前殿叄楹數維如舊<g ref="#CB02420"/>模過之始于嘉靖癸巳春二月
<lb ed="B" n="0314b14"/>終于乙未冬十月三<g ref="#CB11301"/>年而事竣</p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0314b15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">惠應寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>惠應寺</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0314b16"/><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1601" style="margin-left:1em">在都門外南城梅岡北去所領永興寺半里聚寶門三
<lb ed="B" n="0314b17"/>里正德年建今漸傾塌不支</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0314b18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1803" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">金剛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1807" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">金剛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">天王殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1812" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">天王殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1817" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">伍楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左伽藍殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1821" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左伽藍殿<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0314b19"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右祖師殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1901" style="margin-left:2em">右祖師殿<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">法堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1907" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">法堂<note place="inline">伍楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右輪蔵殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1911" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右輪蔵殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1917" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">貳房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址伍拾畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0314b1921" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址伍拾
<lb ed="B" n="0314b20"/>畆<note place="inline">東至普照寺　南至舒家山脚　西至曹家山　北至張百戶墻</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0315a" n="0315a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0315a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">安隱院</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>安隱院</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0315a02"/><p xml:id="pB29p0315a0201" style="margin-left:1em">在都門外南城聚寶山之陽東去所領永興寺半里西
<lb ed="B" n="0315a03"/>北去聚寶門三里正德間剏</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0315a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0315a0403" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">壹座</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0315a0407" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右彌勒殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0315a0411" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右彌勒殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0315a0417" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">貳房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址伍畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0315a0421" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址伍畆
<lb ed="B" n="0315a05"/><note place="inline">東至岳家墳　西至蔣太監埂邊<g ref="#CB29874"/>程御史墳百丈　南至宮街　北至寶光寺墻</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
